last_episode_to_air.name: Father Christmas
last_episode_to_air.overview: Shocking news and unexpected gifts are in store on Christmas Eve as couples and families come together despite their differences.

name: Virgin River
overview: After seeing an ad for a midwife, a recently divorced big-city nurse moves to the redwood forests of California, where she meets an intriguing man.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Engagement. Babies. Heartbreak. Murder. For a small town, Virgin River has its fair share of drama — and Mel Monroe is often in the middle of it.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: Mel and her loved ones in Virgin River support each other while facing all sorts of troubles: death, a fire, custody arguments, breakups and more.

seasons.name: Season 4
seasons.overview: Mel navigates her new reality, Jack's past threatens his future, and new faces arrive — and stir things up — in Virgin River.

seasons.name: Season 5
seasons.overview: Mel adjusts to a different pace of life, Jack works to grow his business, and the town faces new threats as secrets begin to surface in Virgin River.

episodes.name: Carry On
episodes.overview: When nurse practitioner Mel moves to a remote town in northern California looking for a new life, she's startled by the welcome she receives.

episodes.name: Lost
episodes.overview: After finding an abandoned baby on Doc Mullins's doorstep, Mel and her boss argue over whether to call Social Services or find the newborn's mother.

episodes.name: ... and Found
episodes.overview: Mel considers being a temporary foster parent to Chloe while grappling with her own grief. Jack works to convince her to stay in Virgin River.

episodes.name: A Wounded Heart
episodes.overview: Hope's health scare prompts a difficult conversation with Doc. Charmaine asks Mel uncomfortable questions. Paige keeps secrets.

episodes.name: Under Fire
episodes.overview: Under pressure, Mel and Jack respond to a medical emergency on a remote illegal pot farm. Charmaine and Hope exchange words.

episodes.name: Let's Mingle
episodes.overview: Mel gets a surprise visitor just in time for the town's big dance party. Jack continues to suffer flashbacks from his time in the military.

episodes.name: If Truth Be Told
episodes.overview: Preacher happens upon a secret. Mel's memories threaten to overwhelm her. Jack has a sincere talk with Charmaine about their relationship.

episodes.name: Into the Light
episodes.overview: A storm causes a town power outage and everybody gets together at Jack's bar. Mel grapples with her revelation. Preacher investigates Paige.

episodes.name: Everybody Has a Secret
episodes.overview: Hope urges Jack to read Charmaine's letter. Preacher confronts Paige with his new knowledge. Mel and Doc work together on a pressing case.

episodes.name: Unexpected Endings
episodes.overview: Charmaine tells a stunned Jack to make a decision while Mel is left reeling and Hope is filled with guilt. Meanwhile, Paige opens up to Preacher.

episodes.name: New Beginnings
episodes.overview: Jack asks Mel for help when Charmaine experiences a complication in her pregnancy. Hope insists that Doc keep their relationship a secret.

episodes.name: Taken by Surprise
episodes.overview: Despite Mel's efforts, Charmaine's stay at Hope's house gets off to a rocky start. A situation involving Paige's past intensifies unexpectedly.

episodes.name: The Morning After
episodes.overview: Mel endeavors to help an uncooperative Charmaine get hydrated while thinking about what transpired with Jack. Calvin offers Brady a new job.

episodes.name: Rumor Has It
episodes.overview: The town attends the annual picnic where residents engage in friendly competition, romantic tiffs and —as far as Mel is concerned — too much gossip

episodes.name: Can't Let Go
episodes.overview: Jack's war memories haunt him when he reunites with his Marine friends. Mel struggles to handle conflict with her sister-in-law.

episodes.name: Out of the Past
episodes.overview: Mel grapples with how to honor Mark ahead of the anniversary of his death. Jack's stress leads him to bad decisions. Hope apologizes with pie.

episodes.name: Breaking Point
episodes.overview: When police find a body in the woods, Preacher worries about the implications. Charmaine and Jack work on a birth plan with Mel.

episodes.name: Blindspots
episodes.overview: While Jack helps Mike zero in on Calvin, Mel and Doc investigate a mysterious outbreak that could be related to food poisoning. Hope learns a secret.

episodes.name: Hazards Ahead
episodes.overview: Mel searches desperately for Jack, who has stumbled upon disturbing news. Jamie makes Preacher an enticing job offer. Hope questions Doc's loyalty.

episodes.name: Blown Away
episodes.overview: Mel tracks down Brady to find out more about Spencer. Hope answers Doc's question. Preacher makes a life-changing decision.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: Engagement. Babies. Heartbreak. Murder. For a small town, Virgin River has its fair share of drama — and Mel Monroe is often in the middle of it.

episodes.name: Where There's Smoke...
episodes.overview: Mel attempts to avoid celebrating her birthday while remembering the past. Doc confirms his troubling diagnosis and begins looking for his replacement.

episodes.name: Sticky Feet
episodes.overview: Ricky and Lizzie struggle to find privacy. Doc worries about Hope, who may be stuck in a hurricane. Mel offers Jack an enticing invitation.

episodes.name: Spare Parts and Broken Hearts
episodes.overview: Lily divulges a devastating secret to Mel. Brie gets to know Brady better and admits something to Jack. Lizzie's ex surprises her.

episodes.name: Take My Breath Away
episodes.overview: Doc and Mel help Christopher and Preacher with a medical emergency. After an angry confrontation, Jack focuses his energy on a romantic gesture.

episodes.name: Kindling
episodes.overview: Mel is taken aback by Doc's news after they interview a new doctor. To Jack's chagrin, Todd makes a bold request. Lily makes a difficult revelation.

episodes.name: Jack and Jill
episodes.overview: Jack and Mel argue about their relationship and their future while competing in the Lumberjack Games. Brie opens up about her painful breakup.

episodes.name: Split
episodes.overview: Jack meets with a custody attorney and his stress begins to overwhelm him. Brady gets brought in for questioning. Muriel offers Doc advice.

episodes.name: Life and Death
episodes.overview: Heartbroken, Mel heads to LA to support Joey at her divorce hearing. More of Jack's memories return. Lily asks her friends to care for her children.

episodes.name: The Sun Also Rises
episodes.overview: The town says goodbye to a dear friend. Brie suffers a loss of her own. Mel and Jack discuss what should happen with their relationship.

episodes.name: A Wedding, No Funeral and a Baby
episodes.overview: Jack makes a momentous decision as Mel grapples with how to share surprising news. Doc is plagued with concern. Preacher meets with Paige's friend.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: Mel and her loved ones in Virgin River support each other while facing all sorts of troubles: death, a fire, custody arguments, breakups and more.

episodes.name: Be My Baby
episodes.overview: Mel seeks medical care, with a nervous Jack by her side. Hope's confusion puts Doc in a tough position. A new doctor joins the practice.

episodes.name: Father Knows Best...?
episodes.overview: Jack and Brie's father causes friction when he comes into town. An incident at work affects Mel. Doc gets to know his unexpected visitor.

episodes.name: Grilled
episodes.overview: Mel plans a dinner for Cameron to meet Jack, but plans go awry. Connie warns Lizzie to be careful with Denny. Preacher befriends his aikido teacher.

episodes.name: Serious As A...
episodes.overview: Hope's concussive symptoms continue, frustrating both her and Doc. Meanwhile, Mel asks Preacher to help her surprise a stubborn Jack.

episodes.name: Mayday
episodes.overview: After Hope and friends sew the costumes, Lizzie and Ricky rehearse for the Renaissance Fair. Brie and Mike team up to investigate who paid Brady's bond.

episodes.name: All's Faire...
episodes.overview: The Renaissance Fair kicks off. Mel worries about Jack after a familiar face triggers painful memories. Denny watches Lizzie and Ricky perform.

episodes.name: Otherwise Engaged
episodes.overview: Joey arrives with some shocking news that has Mel questioning her sister's judgment. Jack brainstorms a new revenue stream.

episodes.name: Talk to Me
episodes.overview: Mel plans a surprise for Joey but is distracted by her concern for Jack. Lizzie struggles with telling Doc what she saw in Denny's drawer.

episodes.name: Bombshells
episodes.overview: Mel deals with the aftermath of Jack's disappearance while also getting troubling news from Stacie. Mike and Brie continue their search for Calvin.

episodes.name: Fire and Rain
episodes.overview: Charmaine asks Jack for support at the baby shower. Mel has a tough conversation with Cassandra. Preacher worries about Christopher after their call.

episodes.name: Once Again
episodes.overview: Vernon and Hope argue about seeking in-home care, Mel confronts Cameron about his odd behavior, and Jack gets his glamping Airstream up and running.

episodes.name: The Long Goodbye
episodes.overview: Mel and Jack finally receive the results they've been waiting on. Lizzie organizes a send-off for Ricky before speaking to Denny about his secret.

4.name: Season 4
4.overview: Mel navigates her new reality, Jack's past threatens his future, and new faces arrive — and stir things up — in Virgin River.

episodes.name: A Second Chance
episodes.overview: Mel makes a tough decision. Jack draws a potential business investor. Preacher and Paige wonder if they're on the same page. A council meeting stuns Hope.

episodes.name: Songbird
episodes.overview: Doc and Cameron try to run the clinic together. Mel supports Ava through a personal dilemma. Jack confronts Charmaine. Brady seeks a second chance.

episodes.name: Calculated Risk
episodes.overview: Mel makes an exception for a former patient. Brie opens up to Brady. Preacher meets a charming firefighter. Jack goes mountain climbing with Denny.

episodes.name: Never Gonna Be The Same
episodes.overview: Doc confides in Denny. Hope's spa day takes a turn. A desperate Brady reaches out to Mike. On a camping trip, Mel and Jack learn more about each other.

episodes.name: Trial by Fire
episodes.overview: As danger closes in, Jack, Hope and other residents take action. A discovery puts Mel on edge. Brie sees a friendly face after a tense day in court.

episodes.name: Heroes Rise
episodes.overview: Mel and Jack race to bring Ava and Chloe to safety. As the crisis intensifies, Brady defies Preacher, while Hope proposes a plan to save Virgin River.

episodes.name: From the Ashes
episodes.overview: The devastation brings revelations and reconciliations as the community attempts to rebuild and lift each other up after the fires.

episodes.name: Full Moon
episodes.overview: After a girls' night, Mel struggles to let go of her fears. Kaia opens up to Preacher. Mike and Brady set aside their differences to nab a criminal.

episodes.name: Angel's Peak
episodes.overview: Mel and Jack explore other possibilities for their future. Brady follows Melissa and lands in an awkward position. Romance is in the air at the clinic.

episodes.name: Labor Day
episodes.overview: Tensions escalate as Brady, Jack and Mike get caught in the crosshairs of an illicit scheme. More surprises emerge for Mel, Denny and Preacher.

episodes.name: The More the Merrier
episodes.overview: As the holidays get underway, visiting relatives bring drama to town. Mel and Jack try to track down the author of the mysterious letters to her mother.

episodes.name: Father Christmas
episodes.overview: Shocking news and unexpected gifts are in store on Christmas Eve as couples and families come together despite their differences.

5.name: Season 5
5.overview: Mel adjusts to a different pace of life, Jack works to grow his business, and the town faces new threats as secrets begin to surface in Virgin River.
